    "bits), which must be chosen such that, for any subset B ⊆ A 0,..., A m-1, the sum of the matrices in the subset B has rank at least n -r for some small constant r (which acts as a penalty to the output length).",
    "The extractor output of m bits is thenDodis et al.",
